 ing one-hot encoding or label encoding.\n• Create at least two new featu
 res (e.g.\, combining columns\, deriving new information from existing col
 umns).\n\n* Document the steps taken to transform the data and the rationa
 le behind each decision.\n\n* Submit a pdf which includes the following tw
 o items: documented steps in #3 above and a screenshot of your code (this 
 can be partial\, just give us an idea of your work).\n\nNote: These activi
 ties are meant to take 1-2 hours. If you find yourself spending much more 
 time than this please come to office hours for help\, take a break\, or se
 arch for resources online.
