DESCRIPTION:Unit 5 Progress\n\nIcon Progress Bar/Navigation (built in brows
 er\, hidden in app)\n\n \n\n----\nTASK\n----\n\nYour task for this discus
 sion is to review one or two of the following articles. You will then post
  a few sentences or an outline of your discussion below! We will have an i
 n-class discussion. \n\n* [AI Ethics: Challenges\, Importance\, and Futur
 e] (https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/ai-ethics/?ref=header_search)\n\n* [The 
 Ethics of AI: Navigating the Challenges in Responsible Development] (https
 ://www.geeksforgeeks.org/the-ethics-of-ai-navigating-the-challenges-in-res
 ponsible-development/?ref=header_search)\n\n* [Future of AI and Data Scien
 ce] (https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/future-of-ai-and-data-science/?ref=head
 er_search)\n\n-----------------------\nDISCUSSION REQUIREMENTS\n----------
 -------------\n\nOnce you have completed reviewing one or two of the above
  articles\, you are asked to post a 1-2 sentence response or outline of yo
 ur thoughts or something new your learned from the reading. If you need so
 me help or would like to use one of the following prompts to get the creat
 ive juices flowing:\n\n* Questions based on the article "AI Ethics: Challe
 nges\, Importance\, and Future":\n\n* What is the significance of AI ethic
 s in the development and deployment of artificial intelligence systems?\n\
 n* How can developers mitigate bias in AI systems to promote fairness?\n\n
 * Questions based on the article "The Ethics of AI: Navigating the Challen
 ges in Responsible Development":\n\n* What are the primary ethical concern
 s associated with the development and deployment of AI systems?\n\n* How c
 an developers ensure the responsible development of AI technologies?\n\n* 
 Questions based on the article "Future of AI and Data Science":\n\n* How a
 re AI and data science expected to influence various industries in the fut
 ure?\n\n* What ethical considerations are associated with the advancement 
 of AI and data science?\n\n* Provide a free response: this can be anything
  from something that piqued your interest\, or may be a personal experienc
 e you have with what was discussed in the articles.\n\nOur goal is to help
  you get a deeper understanding of data science and discussions are a wond
 erful way to do this! Think of this as a learning opportunity for both you
 \, your classmates\, and your professor! Be sure to use academic language 
 and question ideas from the readings for clarity or to push your own think
 ing.  \n\n-------\nGRADING\n-------\n\nThis assignment is worth a total 
 of 15 points.
