 ode (this can be partial\, just give us an idea of your work).</li>\n</ol>
 \n<p><strong>Note:</strong> These activities are meant to take 1-2 hours. 
 If you find yourself spending much more time than this please come to offi
 ce hours for help\, take a break\, or search for resources online.</p><scr
 ipt src="https://instructure-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/account_980200000000
 00001/attachments/7108467/dp_app%20%25281%2529.js"></script>
