 sidering)\n\n*\n\nText Submission (Discussion Board Post):\n\n* Must addre
 ss the points listed above (objectives\, challenges\, data).\n\n* Keep it 
 clear and concise (a short paragraph or a short bullet list is fine).\n\nB
 e sure you have reviewed the [Applied Data Science Project Introduction] (
 https://elearning.mines.edu/courses/76742/pages/applied-data-science-proje
 ct-introduction) and then post a discussion and a reply below.\n\nOverview
 : For the proposal\, it is expected you submit an initial discussion post 
 that comprehensively outlines your project's objectives\, the methodology 
 you plan to use\, the data sources you intend to draw from\, and the outco
 mes you anticipate achieving. This post should provide a clear and detaile
 d plan for your project\, demonstrating that you have thoroughly thought t
 hrough each aspect of the work you will undertake. \n\nNote: Like any goo
 d research project\, it may evolve as you gather more information. Please 
 use this assignment to organize your thoughts!\n\n-------\nGRADING\n------
 -\n\nThe grade will be comprised of presenting in class and posting your d
 iscussion here.
