 k inline_disabled" src="https://elearning.mines.edu/courses/76742/files/80
 63819/download" alt="scissors sample" width="85" height="85" data-api-endp
 oint="https://elearning.mines.edu/api/v1/courses/76742/files/8063819" data
 -api-returntype="File" loading="lazy"></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>
 \n<hr style="color: #92a2bd\; border: 1px solid\;">\n<h2 class="p1">SUBMIT
 TING YOUR SOLUTION</h2>\n<p class="p1">Submit your notebook file(s). To su
 bmit your notebook\, first clear all the cells (this won't matter too much
  this time\, but for larger data sets in the future\, it will make the fil
 e smaller). Then use the File-&gt\;Download As-&gt\;Notebook to obtain the
