 6/ethics-in-algorithms-highlights-from-cathy-oneils-keynote-at-the-volunte
 er-summit/) from 2021)\n\n* Or visit her [mathbabe.org] (https://mathbabe.
 org/) blog for lots of discussion over the last several years\n\n2. Find A
 nother Data Science Ethical Example\n-------------------------------------
 -------\n\nIdentify another example\, issue\, or case study related to eth
 ics in big data. This could be from a news article\, an academic paper\, a
 n organization’s controversial use of data\, or another reputable source
 .\n\n3. Prepare a Case Study Paper\n-----------------------------\n\nProvi
