 ur example/issue/case study of ethics in big data\n\n* Thoughts provoked b
 y the Ted Talk and your example/issue/case study\n\n* Pros / cons / opinon
 s\n\n4. In-Class Discussion & Peer Reflection\n---------------------------
 -------------\n\nIn class you will be expected to share a quick overview o
 f your ethics case study and share with the class. We will use the time to
  discuss and debate important topics:\n\n* Present or briefly share a brie
 f explanation and key takeaways from your paper.\n\n* Listen to and engage
  with your classmates’ examples.\n\nGRADING\n-------\n\nThis assignment 
 is worth a total of 100 points this is split into 70 points for the paper 
 assignment\, 30 points for attendance and participation in class.
