DESCRIPTION:Unit 5 Progress\n\nIcon Progress Bar/Navigation (built in brows
 er\, hidden in app)\n\n \n\n----\nTASK\n----\n\nYour task for this assign
 ment is to complete and submit the results and evaluation section for your
  applied data science project: it is critical to understand the results of
  your experiments and determine if refinements can be made for this iterat
 ive process.\n\nBe sure you have reviewed the [Applied Data Science Proje
 ct Introduction.] (https://elearning.mines.edu/courses/76742/pages/applied
 -data-science-project-introduction)\n\nOverview: Present the results of yo
 ur model\, including a detailed discussion of the evaluation metrics used 
 to assess performance. Provide a comprehensive comparison of the different
  models you have developed\, highlighting their strengths and weaknesses b
 ased on these metrics. Include visual aids such as graphs\, tables\, and c
 harts to illustrate your findings clearly as needed. This section should p
 rovide a thorough analysis of the outcomes\, demonstrating your ability to
  critically evaluate and interpret the performance of your models.\n\nSubm
 ission:\n\nPlease submit a pdf\, doc or docx file that includes your analy
 sis\, some screenshots and possibly some code related to your results.\n\n
 To see the specific grading criteria for this assignment\, please view the
  rubric.
